In the case where the new perturbation leads to the improvement of the economic sectors, the inoperability level follows a decreasing trend that could be modeled by linking the inoperability at time t to the inoperability level at time t − 1. This could be constructed mathematically as follows:8\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
